8, \"to\": 402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is what you need to know about the ceremony: Organizers have promised a show like no other and said it would be daring and joyful.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"Organizers\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"a show\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time, the opening ceremony will not take place in a stadium.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, dozens of boats will carry thousands of athletes and performers on a 6-kilometer floating parade on the Seine.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.923259974429783e-18, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6-kilometer floating parade\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Departing from the Austerlitz bridge, they will sail by Notre-Dame de Paris cathedral and arrive near the Eiffel Tower, after passing under bridges and gateways, including the Pont des Arts and Pont Neuf, and near many of the French capital's landmarks.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 787