 2202, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"the committee\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizing the ceremony in the heart of an iconic city like Paris may make for great pictures, but it's also a major security challenge.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2300, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.431725006335645e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"an iconic city\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"great pictures\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"a major security challenge\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 45,000 police will be dispatched to ensure the ceremony's security, including special intervention forces.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some 45,000 police\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's security\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"special intervention forces\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snipers will be deployed on the top of buildings along the route.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Snipers\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An anti-drone system will be in place.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An anti-drone system\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spectators and local residents alike will need to carry permits on a QR code to get anywhere near the riverbanks from July 18.\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spectators\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"local residents\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"permits\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"a QR code\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverbanks\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cars will not be allowed into the area, with few exceptions.\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cars\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"few exceptions\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearby metro stations will be closed, as will many of the bridges.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"metro stations\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridges\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No planes will be allowed to fly over Paris - unless they are part of the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2890, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.431725006335645e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No planes\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With wars in Gaza and Ukraine, and security concerns at home, France already has its security alert at its highest level.\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2954, \"title\": \"http://db